<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
    <title>Home</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="w-full min-h-screen bg-gray-800 text-white flex items-center justify-center flex-col gap-5">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">This is Home Page 🏠🏡</h1>
        <h1>Using EJS we can also do the dynamic printing:</h1>
        <p>
            2+2: <%= 2+ 2 %>
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-5 flex-col">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-5">
                <button id="inc-btn" class="hover:cursor-pointer hover:scale-105 bg-blue-400 text-black p-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-xl">
                    + ve
